issue.title: Convert to use venv virtualenv and update documentation
issue.body:
When I wrote this I hardcoded my instance of python2 into the export-chatbot.sh script.

It's an easy one, could someone make a configuration for venv, document it in the README and ensure the environment is added to .gitignore :)

It might require changing up the section in the README on **Exporting bot-definition**. Feel free to get creative
